{"tid":2377342,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"女神私處傳異味　內地男頂唔順嗌：嗚哇！好臭！　床邊作嘔3分鐘","createTime":"2021-01-23T14:05:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T14:20:18.000Z","uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"35ac715e41681e4502e34265bcd7c2264b79262c","tid":2377342,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T14:05:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/yyt2GQX17p0NXzR4mz28AWLnttU=/760x428/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RSGDBHJ7H5ADLLQD6COXIR5EVM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fyyt2GQX17p0NXzR4mz28AWLnttU%3D%2F760x428%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRSGDBHJ7H5ADLLQD6COXIR5EVM.jpg&h=179c8050&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n該片段近日於討論區瘋傳，引起網民熱議，片段標題指該對男女是床伴，早前相約到酒店歡好，在床上纏綿期間，男子突然問女伴：「怎麼紅的啊？沒月經嗎？」女子即時否認，又要求他繼續。沒料這時男子忍不住直呼：「嗚哇！好臭！」然後在旁邊作嘔。<br />\n<br />\n男方一直作嘔，甚至一度躺下休息，更直接詢問女方「是不是有風流病」。女子聞言否認，反駁稱可能是「血的味道」，又指自己有清潔私處。然而男子未有停止作嘔，其間又崩潰稱：「妳這是什麼味啊！」過了約3分鐘，男子休息過後才回復精神，稍作清潔後決定忍臭繼續纏綿。<br />\n<br />\n片段被上載至成人網站引起網民注意，有人看完整個過程感到非常好奇，不禁於討論區發文詢問：「真的會臭到讓人想吐？」帖文引出不少「老手」，有人認真分享，稱個人衛生習慣非常重要，一旦私處遭到感染或會引來「恐怖」後果，「有碰過很認真洗過了，還是有味道的，沒洗的聞到會死人」、「真的會，細菌感染的話會超臭」。<br />\n<br />\n亦有網民「錯重點」，笑指片中男子是「勇士」，不明白他為何能忍受味道繼續激戰，「聽那乾嘔聲，我都覺得我好像聞到那臭味了」、「快笑死！他還做得下去喔」、「看他嘔的樣子，應該真的很臭」。亦有網民質疑片段屬炒作，旨在吸引人氣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3778978/org/2801db0ec88a99e59e5b2f2bd140a620.jpg/cX_9ljSk5bdmYB5CIaSjFqLFtkc9gXdOpEafzqRGn84?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3778978%2Forg%2F2801db0ec88a99e59e5b2f2bd140a620.jpg%2FcX_9ljSk5bdmYB5CIaSjFqLFtkc9gXdOpEafzqRGn84%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=c8c283d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3778979/org/2e684ef469296aec6b7413d3521c356d.jpg/yIvWaGEymaSjCK-vEEA2eBSvs7W6QkI718Y4DtfGOA4?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3778979%2Forg%2F2e684ef469296aec6b7413d3521c356d.jpg%2FyIvWaGEymaSjCK-vEEA2eBSvs7W6QkI718Y4DtfGOA4%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=1cdb2567&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3778980/org/0ea1b84ec40f0b704c6092aa4bf3830d.jpg/zxGUkfkB-91zXUQA2pyd6Jqzkjt-tU8xxuuW7Mbrluw?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3778980%2Forg%2F0ea1b84ec40f0b704c6092aa4bf3830d.jpg%2FzxGUkfkB-91zXUQA2pyd6Jqzkjt-tU8xxuuW7Mbrluw%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=f091cb6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3778985/org/b6205fbe0c99d306213092dcfd7bb59f.jpg/BSgVICL9XiDpGf_gQns-6hr6lfvbKlhxLyNjbi8jY24?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3778985%2Forg%2Fb6205fbe0c99d306213092dcfd7bb59f.jpg%2FBSgVICL9XiDpGf_gQns-6hr6lfvbKlhxLyNjbi8jY24%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=73f83881&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1cac7f221ecfdb6c9c196502046937d93022904b","tid":2377342,"uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T14:08:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.pornhub.com/view_video.php?viewkey=ph600010d303a24\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pornhub.com%2Fview_video.php%3Fviewkey%3Dph600010d303a24&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TahZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=c4e30f84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pornhub.com/view_video.php?viewkey=ph600010d303a24</a>"},{"pid":"f872a822d98b467dc775ef73c50464e519f63bfa","tid":2377342,"uid":185142,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T14:08:26.000Z","msg":"大佬啊，我以為出第2集啦。<br />\n<br />\n點知樓主仲做緊回帶西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"906010cfb5693f8bc55288f296710494bc49f88b","tid":2377342,"uid":373438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cac7f221ecfdb6c9c196502046937d93022904b